    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I think people would really appreciate some more specific details though, especially when it comes to grooming and hair. Could you expand on that? Like, what kind of hairstyles or grooming habits would you recommend to ensure someone looks truly polished and \"boardroom ready\"?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
