      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For men, a neat, short haircut that is meticulously maintained is essential; anything too trendy or long looks unprofessional. Facial hair, if worn, must be perfectly trimmed and sculpted, not scruffy. Women should aim for hairstyles that are neat and controlled, whether worn up or down, avoiding anything overly voluminous or distracting. Overall, the grooming should suggest discipline and attention to detail, which is what executives are expected to project.",
      "source": "target",
